{"sn15.14:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 15.14 ","sn15.14:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn15.14:0.3":"Matusutta ","sn15.14:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn15.14:1.2":"“Anamataggoyam, bhikkhave, samsaro …pe… ","sn15.14:1.3":"na so, bhikkhave, satto sulabharupo yo namatabhutapubbo imina dighena addhuna. ","sn15.14:1.4":"Tam kissa hetu? ","sn15.14:1.5":"Anamataggoyam, bhikkhave, samsaro …pe… ","sn15.14:1.6":"alam vimuccitun”ti. ","sn15.14:1.7":"Catuttham. "}